es wizard melee output bringing them from 5 to 10 dpm, and it's still balanced, yet for rogues you might have to give a very incremental increase of 5% or 10% so they don't destroy the balance of the game.<br><br>Just to further the thought, do you know that there are currently no rogue piercers that are usable in the primary hand with a base damage of over 15 or possibly 16?  That's because with a backstab ability, the multiplier is HUGE and a 20 damage backstabber would be way too powerful.  Yet there are tons of weapons that have a damage rating of 40, 50, or higher that are usable by the other melee classes who don't have backstab.<br><br>Anyway, enough rambling for me, but look at the big picture.  They aren't doing it to laugh at you, they are trying to keep the game playable or we'd all make rogues.<br><br>Isthoss/Eldan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub47.ezboard.com/uaalaandro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aalaandro</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fluffy </span><br>  Posts: 1945<br> <font color=#ffff00>(4/16/02 2:30:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=678.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: whyyyyyy!</span><hr size=1> I stick by what I said.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Aalaandro has slain Isthoss.<br>Aalaandro has slain Kirche.<br><br>Nuff said. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52938"> My Equipment</a> <img src="http://sigs-by-sy.netfirms.com/aal-new-sig.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign